Package: bayestraitr
Type: Package
Title: A set of tools to help with the interpretation and analysis of the output
of BayesTraits MCMC analyses.
Version: 0.0.1
Author: Henry Ferguson-Gow
Maintainer: Henry Ferguson-Gow <henry.fergusongow@gmail.com>
Description: This package contains a set of functions to help with the 
summarisation, visualisation and manipulation of the posterior that BayesTraits
returns when run in MCMC mode. It includes functions to summarise and visualise
the results of models that use the variable rates and variable transformation
functionality of BayesTraits, and various functions to plot these results on
phylogenies.
License: What license is it under?
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
